    "text": "Halting Of Trafficking and Exploitation in Lodging Act of 2022 or the HOTEL Act of 2022\n\nThis bill requires federal agencies to ensure, to the greatest extent practicable, that commercial accommodations for agency employees are booked with a hotel or motel that enforces a zero-tolerance policy regarding severe forms of trafficking in persons."
